OL,4,Cvan driver under influence of drugs
OL,6,FA van driver who reversed into a 94-
OL,7,Fyear-old woman, leaving her with fatal
OL,8,Finjuries, has been sent to prison.
OL,10,FThe collision happened at around
OL,11,F12.50pm on Tuesday 2 May 2023. Belinda
OL,12,FBenley was crossing the road in
OL,13,FWooland Gardens in Wyke Regis when a
OL,14,FMercedes Sprinter van, which was
OL,15,Freversing, hit her.
OL,17,FMs Bentley died at the scene as a
OL,18,Fresult of her injuries.
