OL,3,CPensioner killed after being hit by
OL,4,Cvan driver under influence of drugs
OL,6,FEdgaras Kondratas, 41 and from
OL,7,FSouthampton, was arrested and failed a
OL,8,Fdrug test when analysis of his blood
OL,9,Fsample showed the presence of Delta-9-
OL,10,Ftetrahydrocannabinol (THC), a
OL,11,Fpsychoactive constituent of cannabis.
OL,13,FHe had a concentration of 2.8
OL,14,Fmicrograms per litre of blood, above
OL,15,Fthe legal limit of two micrograms.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
