OL,3,CPensioner killed after being hit by
OL,4,Cvan driver under influence of drugs
OL,6,FKondratas said had checked his mirrors
OL,7,Fbefore reversing, but had not looked
OL,8,Fat his rear-view camera, which would
OL,9,Fhave shown the victim behind his
OL,10,Fvehicle. The rear parking sensors on
OL,11,Fthe van were also not in working order.
OL,13,FKondratas appeared at Winchester Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Friday 6 December 2024 after
OL,15,Fbeing found guilty of causing death by
OL,16,Fdriving without due care and
OL,17,Fconsideration while over the specified
OL,18,Flimit for a controlled drug.
