OL,6,FHe was sentenced to three years in
OL,7,Fprison and disqualified from driving
OL,8,Ffor three years following his release
OL,9,Ffrom prison.
OL,11,FFollowing the sentencing hearing, the
OL,12,Ffamily of Belinda said in a statement:
OL,13,F"My mother was killed on a bright
OL,14,Fsummer's day while walking, close to
OL,15,Fthe home she had lived in for almost
OL,16,F30 years.
