OL,3,CPensioner killed after being hit by
OL,4,Cvan driver under influence of drugs
OL,6,F"The place she died is a popular
OL,7,Fwalking route for children, families,
OL,8,Fdog walkers; a place that she, and
OL,9,FWyke Regis people of all ages,
OL,10,Fconsider quiet and safe.
OL,12,F"I hope anyone reading this story is
OL,13,Freminded when they are driving to
OL,14,Falways always take care, be constantly
OL,15,Fobservant, and to allow for the
OL,16,Funexpected, however quiet, and
OL,17,Fpeaceful the road.
OL,19,F"My mum is missed, every day, by her
OL,20,Ffamily and her many friends, and her
OL,21,Fneighbours in Wooland Gardens."
