OL,6,FPolice Constable Leanne Howes, of
OL,7,FDorset Police's Serious Collision
OL,8,FInvestigation Team, said: "Edgaras
OL,9,FKondratas' inconsiderate driving while
OL,10,Fover the specified drug limit has had
OL,11,Fdevastating consequences, resulting in
OL,12,Fthe death of a much-loved woman.
OL,14,F"This case is an example of how a
OL,15,Fcareless omission to check a rear-view
OL,16,Fcamera before carrying out a manoeuvre
OL,17,Fin a van can result in a tragic
OL,18,Foutcome.
