OL,6,F"We want to highlight the importance
OL,7,Fto all motorists of ensuring they
OL,8,Fdrive with diligence and remain
OL,9,Fvigilant to all road users when behind
OL,10,Fthe wheel of a vehicle.
OL,12,F"We remain committed to doing
OL,13,Feverything we can to ensure those who
OL,14,Fdrive without due care and
OL,15,Fconsideration while under the
OL,16,Finfluence and flout road traffic laws
OL,17,Fare identified and brought before the
OL,18,Fcourts."
